description: The ID of this Google Search result.
name: id

description: The ID of the Google Search instance to which this search result belongs.
name: base_id

description: The list index of the search result.
name: list_index

description: The type to which this search result belongs (can be a promoted search result of either the top or bottom of the page, a snippet, or a non-promoted result).
name: type

description: The title of the search result.
name: title

description: The source URL of the search result.
name: source_url

description: The publisher's website URL of the search result.
name: publisher_url

description: The stripped HTML of the search result's body; also contains the text of the description.
name: stripped_html_HTML

description: The URLs obtained from the 'stripped_html_HTML' field.
name: stripped_html_source_urls

description: The images (as Base64 strings or URLs) obtained from the 'stripped_html_HTML' field.
name: stripped_html_media_thumbnail_urls

description: The time of publication of the search result (which is usually presented with articles or news stories).
name: time_of_publication
